          "\\(\\frac{x - h}{x(x+h)}\\)"
        ],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "f(x+h)-f(x) = 1/(x+h) - 1/x = (x - (x+h))/(x(x+h)) = -h/(x(x+h))"
